lead_paragraph: Donovan McNabb should not expect a “get well soon” text message from Terrell Owens. “Absolutely not,” Owens said yesterday. Although McNabb has said he reached out to Owens after his brief hospital stint for an accidental overdose in September, Owens has maintained he never received anything from McNabb. “I’m not even going there, dude,” Owens said”.
